name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of deadly punks with superpowers are assigned a mysterious mission.  
Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center.For now,the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #016
Female

Name         : Renvoine
Strength     : 85/100
Intelligence : 96/100

She was the queen of Amfethi. She along with nine of the ministers planned the assassination of the princess Remeira and were caught. They were fed to the cerberus, the 3 headed monster. Her soul was released from the underworld by the Gurhav twins.
